description: This is simple: We have a sexy, cute, hot, newcomer who really wants to wrestle. We have the Powerhouse Dragon who is going to kick her ass, and fuck her like a slut on the mat. What we do not know yet is how much will the newcomer will learn, and will she be able to apply it to her next match. After the first RD the Badger catches on and picks up the pace. One thing is sure she is a tough little girl.
title: The Dragon (17-5)
